metadata.title: DPM/FM Dar expresses satisfaction over growing Pak-UK ties

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Oct 18 (APP): Deputy Prime Minister/Foreign Minister Senator Mohammad Ishaq Dar on Saturday appreciated the strengthening of Pak-UK ties and the recent leadership-level interactions. The DPM/FM expressed these views during a meeting with United Kingdom High Commissioner Jane Marriott who called on him, Foreign Office Spokesperson said in a press release. They also discussed the regional and global developments.
